school_name: Rutgers - State University of New Jersey
comments: Professor Marano is very easy going. I have her now (spring 09) for Special Topics in Juvenile Justice. She provides powerpoint slides after lecture and exam is multiple choice. You have to do a presentation on a case and do 2 page paper. Professor Marano is easy to approach. I highly recommend her and any course she teaches.
